<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SKEC - Course Overview</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

:root {
--bg-black: #05070a;
--teal-bright: #2dd4bf;
--white: #f4faf9;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
min-height: 100vh;
background:
radial-gradient(circle at 90% 10%, rgba(20,184,166,0.55) 0%, rgba(20,184,166,0.15) 30%, transparent 55%),
radial-gradient(circle at 0% 90%, rgba(88,28,135,0.35) 0%, transparent 45%),
var(--bg-black);
font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
padding: 40px 24px;
}

.container {
max-width: 800px;
margin: 0 auto;
}

.header {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.back-btn {
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.2);
border: 1px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.5);
color: var(--teal-bright);
padding: 8px 16px;
border-radius: 8px;
cursor: pointer;
font-weight: 600;
transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.back-btn:hover {
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.4);
border-color: var(--teal-bright);
}

h1 {
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
font-weight: 800;
font-size: 48px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(--teal-bright);
text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(45,212,191,0.4);
}

.modules {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr;
gap: 20px;
}

.module-card {
display: block;
text-decoration: none;
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.06);
border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.5);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 24px;
cursor: pointer;
transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.module-card:hover {
transform: translateX(8px);
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.14);
border-color: var(--teal-bright);
}

.module-number {
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 14px;
color: rgba(45,212,191,0.7);
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: 1px;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.module-title {
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 20px;
color: var(--white);
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.module-desc {
font-size: 14px;
color: rgba(244,250,249,0.7);
line-height: 1.5;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<div class="header">
<button class="back-btn" onclick="window.location.href='index.html'">← Back</button>
<h1>Course Overview</h1>
</div>

<div class="modules">

<a class="module-card" href="module-1.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 1</div>
<div class="module-title">Teacher Standards & Reflections</div>
<div class="module-desc">Understand your role, celebrate your growth, and explore the teacher standards that guide your practice.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-2.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 2</div>
<div class="module-title">Narrative Writing</div>
<div class="module-desc">From common errors to strong models, learn how to teach creative storytelling with write-alongs and practical tasks.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-3.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 3</div>
<div class="module-title">Persuasive Writing</div>
<div class="module-desc">Build arguments from evidence, teach correlation versus causality, and help pupils take a stance.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-4.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 4</div>
<div class="module-title">Analytical Writing</div>
<div class="module-desc">Master the grade boundaries, scaffold with sentence-by-sentence models, and use analytical frameworks.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-5.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 5</div>
<div class="module-title">Literature & Unseen Poetry</div>
<div class="module-desc">Teach themes, comparison, and visual scaffolds like boxes to help pupils unlock unseen poetry.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-6.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 6</div>
<div class="module-title">Macbeth & Romeo and Juliet</div>
<div class="module-desc">Explore character, plot, themes, and writer's intentions across Shakespeare's greatest works.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-7.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 7</div>
<div class="module-title">A Christmas Carol & Jekyll and Hyde</div>
<div class="module-desc">Navigate Victorian literature and the moral dilemmas at the heart of these enduring texts.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-8.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 8</div>
<div class="module-title">An Inspector Calls & Animal Farm</div>
<div class="module-desc">Unpack social responsibility, power, and allegory in these modern classics.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-9.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 9</div>
<div class="module-title">How to Improve People's Writing</div>
<div class="module-desc">Sentence-by-sentence activities, progression strategies, and moving pupils from good to great.</div>
</a>

<a class="module-card" href="module-10.html">
<div class="module-number">Module 10</div>
<div class="module-title">Behaviour for Learning</div>
<div class="module-desc">Create a positive classroom culture and tap into the Behaviour for Learning framework for sustainable change.</div>
</a>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
